Malice/ Organics/ Hellplague/ Splattercannon/ Necross/ Sweeps:

Malice slowly awoke and looked around with clouded optics.  Rodimus had repelled Blacknightmare, Windlord and Blackfang were firing on Necross, and Nightlight had recovered Organics.  Malice tried clear his head, and tried to stand.  All of this, just for him.  Organics was critically damaged, the other Maximals were surely getting tired.  
&quot;Rodimus,&quot; Malice groaned as he got up to one knee,&quot;Let them take me.  There is no sense in all of you to risk it all over me.&quot;

Organics tried to push herself up to see what was going on, but Nightlight held her down and covered he with a wing.  Mechfluid began ooze from various cuts and breaks in her armor.

Hellplague finally had full control of her arms.  SHe cackled as she righted her self and flew toward Malice.
&quot;Necross, Splattercannon!  Help me!  Get that bounty hunter!&quot;
Hellplague, Necross, and Splattercannon approach and open fire with their various weapons, to recover Malice and battle another day.

The remaining Sweeps open fire against the Maximal with new fury.  Their master Hellplague wanted something, and they had to do everything in their power to ensure she got her prize.

